data.title: Chromosome level genome assembly of colored calla lily (Zantedeschia elliottiana)
data.meta_description: The colored calla lily is an ornamental floral plant native to southern Africa, belonging to the Zantedeschia genus of the Araceae family. We generated a high-quality chromosome-level genome of the colored calla lily, with a size of 1,154 Mb and a contig N50 of 42 Mb. We anchored 98.5% of the contig â€¦
